textAnnotations.description:
It seemed to the frightened judge
as though his son would actually
shoot the craft in under the outer
end of the whof. But by pressing
the tilles had over and at the
same time dopping the small sheet
of wet carwas, Bill cleaved the
carnes of the pies by incles, and
with the tille still had oves, brought
the you! up against the waves
